768
00:29:55,750 --> 00:29:57,310
the greater cause in his heart.

769
00:29:57,310 --> 00:29:58,110
Let me tell you,

770
00:29:58,110 --> 00:29:58,930
I saw it.

771
00:29:58,950 --> 00:30:00,840
I saw it very clearly.

772
00:30:00,870 --> 00:30:02,220
I think Zhang Yunkui is

773
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:03,770
just a fool.

774
00:30:03,800 --> 00:30:05,160
I think you, Ding Yujiao, are

775
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:06,810
a fool too.

776
00:30:06,840 --> 00:30:07,900
I'm warning you.

777
00:30:08,250 --> 00:30:09,350
Dare to say

778
00:30:09,350 --> 00:30:10,640
