779
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:12,590
Zhang Yunkui!

780
00:30:12,780 --> 00:30:14,260
Zhang Yunkui! Zhang Yunkui! Zhang Yunkui!

781
00:30:14,260 --> 00:30:15,090
Zhang Yunkui! Zhang Yunkui!

782
00:30:15,090 --> 00:30:16,040
Zhang...

783
00:30:18,750 --> 00:30:20,190
