784
00:30:22,020 --> 00:30:24,580
I told you not to say his name.

785
00:30:25,190 --> 00:30:28,510
Never say his name
for the rest of your life.

786
00:30:29,080 --> 00:30:31,600
You are not worthy.

787
00:30:56,270 --> 00:30:57,750
They started fighting.

788
00:30:57,770 --> 00:30:59,210
If Meng really gets beaten up,

789
00:30:59,210 --> 00:31:00,240
isn't that good?

790
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:04,800
You can't even tell the good guys
from the bad guys.

791
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:07,700
You can't even tell good words
from bad ones.

792
00:31:07,850 --> 00:31:09,360
