795
00:31:12,500 --> 00:31:13,770
If I had sold the sword for money,

796
00:31:13,770 --> 00:31:15,830
I would've arrived in Wuhan long ago.

797
00:31:22,930 --> 00:31:24,940
Hasn't your sword been delivered already?

798
00:31:24,940 --> 00:31:26,000
Then, you have done everything you can

799
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:27,200
