807
00:31:43,690 --> 00:31:45,290
It has nothing to do with you.

808
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:49,410
I shouldn't have cared about you.

809
00:31:50,450 --> 00:31:52,230
Yes, you're right.

810
00:31:52,270 --> 00:31:53,620
The affairs of your Zhang family

811
00:31:53,620 --> 00:31:55,220
