the missing person notices.

813
00:32:10,450 --> 00:32:11,980
Master still owes me money.

814
00:32:12,840 --> 00:32:13,970
Once I get the money,

815
00:32:14,220 --> 00:32:15,880
I'll go to Wuhan immediately.

816
00:32:24,570 --> 00:32:26,480
They act even more real than we do.

817
00:32:26,510 --> 00:32:27,620
It's not acting.

818
00:32:27,650 --> 00:32:28,880
They are really arguing.

819
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:29,720
Nonsense.

820
00:32:29,750 --> 00:32:31,280
They are already fighting.

821
00:32:51,250 --> 00:32:53,640
If you want to feed the kid rice soup,

822
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:56,340
