Food is ready.

842
00:34:47,260 --> 00:34:48,900
Food is ready.

843
00:34:49,010 --> 00:34:49,699
Come.

844
00:34:50,540 --> 00:34:51,310
Here.

845
00:34:51,719 --> 00:34:52,760
