865
00:35:33,860 --> 00:35:35,520
Don't fight, there's enough.

866
00:35:41,040 --> 00:35:41,690
Line up.

867
00:35:42,300 --> 00:35:43,050
Line up.

868
00:35:52,580 --> 00:35:54,580
Don't fight, everyone gets a share.

869
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:03,090
Which jerk cooked this?

870
00:36:03,140 --> 00:36:04,470
Which jerk cooked this?

871
00:36:05,720 --> 00:36:07,350
You jerk cooked this food?

872
