884
00:36:29,190 --> 00:36:30,790
Squad Leader, there is meat.

885
00:36:31,060 --> 00:36:32,390
There is meat in the pot.

886
00:36:32,580 --> 00:36:33,160
There is meat?

887
00:36:33,160 --> 00:36:34,500
Yes, there is meat.

888
00:36:34,620 --> 00:36:36,100
Which of you ate meat?

889
00:36:36,120 --> 00:36:37,220
Whose bowl has meat?

890
00:36:37,220 --> 00:36:37,890
Report to the Squad Leader.

891
00:36:37,890 --> 00:36:39,010
I found meat.

892
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:43,210
You found meat?

893
00:36:44,820 --> 00:36:46,460
You found meat?

894
00:36:47,990 --> 00:36:49,070
