903
00:37:03,850 --> 00:37:04,960
Fight? Fight for what?

904
00:37:04,960 --> 00:37:07,360
How can we fight
with just this little meat?

905
00:37:09,930 --> 00:37:12,220
The Central Army looks down
on our Sichuan Army.

906
00:37:12,220 --> 00:37:13,320
You jerk

907
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:14,850
