908
00:37:14,870 --> 00:37:15,970
No, no.

909
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:16,770
Fine.

910
00:37:17,280 --> 00:37:18,190
Eat it.

911
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:19,730
This won't break your teeth,

912
00:37:19,730 --> 00:37:21,070
