-Squad Leader!

921
00:37:33,640 --> 00:37:34,760
-Squad Leader!
-Squad Leader!

922
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:35,520
Squad Leader of Squad Three.

923
00:37:35,520 --> 00:37:37,050
Squad Leader, are you okay?

924
00:37:37,160 --> 00:37:38,920
