928
00:37:42,100 --> 00:37:42,970
Beat him.

929
00:37:43,000 --> 00:37:43,710
Beat him.

930
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:47,820
You're rebelling.

931
00:37:48,730 --> 00:37:49,810
Beat him to death.

932
00:37:52,830 --> 00:37:54,160
You guys are rebelling.

933
00:37:56,650 --> 00:37:57,490
Go. Go.

934
00:37:57,520 --> 00:37:58,350
Behave.

935
00:37:58,750 --> 00:38:00,380
It's great.

936
00:38:02,130 --> 00:38:02,860
Brother.

937
00:38:03,500 --> 00:38:04,620
My tooth fell out.

938
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:05,990
The Fifth War Area

939
