949
00:38:19,970 --> 00:38:21,500
Is it wrong to defend China?

950
00:38:21,730 --> 00:38:22,880
What do you think we should do?

951
00:38:22,880 --> 00:38:24,470
Beat him to death.

952
00:38:24,550 --> 00:38:25,280
Yes.

953
00:38:25,960 --> 00:38:26,840
Make him kneel.

954
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:27,590
Beat him.

955
00:38:27,720 --> 00:38:28,630
Kneel! Kneel!

956
00:38:28,650 --> 00:38:29,740
Beat him to death.

957
00:38:30,130 --> 00:38:30,610
Kneel!

958
00:38:30,660 --> 00:38:31,700
