975
00:39:15,850 --> 00:39:16,850
It's a long story.

976
00:39:17,510 --> 00:39:18,510
It's a long story.

977
00:39:20,020 --> 00:39:20,850
I understand.

978
00:39:21,330 --> 00:39:22,860
