992
00:39:44,840 --> 00:39:46,070
Did your tooth fall out?

993
00:39:46,070 --> 00:39:46,480
No.

994
00:39:46,500 --> 00:39:47,380
Yours didn't either, right?

995
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:47,780
No.

996
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:48,800
Did you see that?

997
00:39:49,670 --> 00:39:51,200
The nation is in peril.

998
00:39:51,270 --> 00:39:53,780
It's not easy for the Fifth War Area

999
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:55,590
