1004
00:40:01,280 --> 00:40:01,960
Yes.

1005
00:40:02,200 --> 00:40:03,020
Okay.

1006
00:40:03,040 --> 00:40:04,110
It's a misunderstanding.

1007
00:40:04,110 --> 00:40:05,700
Everyone, hurry up and eat.

1008
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:07,280
Brothers, keep eating.

1009
00:40:07,430 --> 00:40:08,210
