1010
00:40:08,240 --> 00:40:09,210
Hurry up and eat.

1011
00:40:09,470 --> 00:40:10,190
Hurry.

1012
00:40:11,700 --> 00:40:13,090
It's a misunderstanding.

1013
00:40:13,090 --> 00:40:14,490
We are all on the same side.

1014
00:40:14,490 --> 00:40:15,220
Right?

1015
00:40:15,370 --> 00:40:16,390
