1026
00:40:43,830 --> 00:40:44,940
Platoon Leader You.

1027
00:40:44,940 --> 00:40:46,130
Zhang Yunkui.

1028
00:40:57,590 --> 00:40:59,860
Sir, we've kept your usual seat.

1029
00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:00,780
Please come in.

1030
00:41:01,070 --> 00:41:01,710
Please.

1031
00:41:02,390 --> 00:41:04,410
[Lutai Restaurant]

1032
00:41:02,590 --> 00:41:05,360
Shandong cuisine.
Authentic Shandong cuisine.
